Depends: ${misc:Depends}, default-jre | java8-runtime, python3, python3-pyqt5, python3-fitz, python3-magic
Replaces: loongoffice-zh-cn, loongofficebasis-zh-cn-help, loongofficebasis-zh-cn, loongoffice-debian-menus, loongoffice-sdk, loongoffice-help-zh-cn
Conflicts: loongoffice-zh-cn, loongofficebasis-zh-cn-help, loongofficebasis-zh-cn, loongoffice-debian-menus, loongoffice-sdk, loongoffice-help-zh-cn
Description: office productivity suite
 LoongOffice is a full-featured office productivity suite with a near
 drop-in replacement for Microsoft(R) Office.
 .
 This package contains the main application with embedded URE runtime,
 including Writer, Calc, Impress, Draw, and Math. It also includes
 Chinese localization, OFD reader extension, SDK for development,
 and Chinese help documentation.
 .
 The package merges all components into a single all-in-one package
 for easier installation and management.
